### Test API Endpoints

### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_full_name": "Arjun Mehta",
  "email": "arjun@example.com",
  "upi_id": "arjun@paytm",
  "allowedNotification": ["email", "push"]
}

### 2. Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### 3. Get User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/USER_ID_HERE

### 4. Create Trip
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/trips
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trip_name": "Manali Adventure 2024",
  "trip_start_date": "2024-10-12",
  "trip_end_date": "2024-10-20",
  "category": "Adventure",
  "members_id": ["USER_ID_1", "USER_ID_2"],
  "trip_cover_image": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

### 5. Get All Trips
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/trips

### 6. Get Trip by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/trips/TRIP_ID_HERE

### 7. Add Member to Trip
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/trips/TRIP_ID_HERE/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### 8. Create Expense
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expense_title": "Dinner at Highway Dhaba",
  "amount": 2450,
  "category": "Food",
  "trip_id": "TRIP_ID_HERE",
  "paid_by_id": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "split_between": [
    {
      "name": "Arjun Mehta",
      "user_id": "USER_ID_1",
      "amount": 490
    },
    {
      "name": "Priya Singh",
      "user_id": "USER_ID_2",
      "amount": 490
    }
  ]
}

### 9. Get Expenses by Trip
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses/trip/TRIP_ID_HERE

### 10. Get Expense Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses/trip/TRIP_ID_HERE/summary

### 11. Calculate Settlement
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/settlements/trip/TRIP_ID_HERE/calculate

### 12. Get Settlement by Trip
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/settlements/trip/TRIP_ID_HERE

### 13. Update Settlement Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/settlements/trip/TRIP_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "settlementIndex": 0,
  "status": "Paid"
}

### 14. Get or Create Chat
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/trip/TRIP_ID_HERE

### 15. Add Message (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripId": "TRIP_ID_HERE",
  "sender_id": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "name": "Arjun Mehta",
  "text": "Hello everyone!"
}

### 16. Get Chat Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/trip/TRIP_ID_HERE/messages
